results.t: Senators Profile - Eulogio A. Rodriguez, Sr.
results.p: Eulogio “Amang” Rodriguez was Municipal President of Montalban, Rizal from 1906-1916; became Governor of Rizal in June 1916; and was reelected in June 1922.
